/a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%EF%BC%8C%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0-GlobalTransactional"><span class="nav-number">6.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">超时异常，添加@GlobalTransactional</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#Seata%E4%B9%8B%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B"><span class="nav-number">7.</span> <span class="nav-text">Seata之原理简介</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#Seata"><span class="nav-number">7.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">Seata</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%86%8D%E7%9C%8BTC-TM-RM%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6"><span class="nav-number">7.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">再看TC&#x2F;TM&#x2F;RM三大组件</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#AT%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E4%BE%B5%E5%85%A5"><span class="nav-number">7.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">AT模式如何做到对业务的无侵入</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85"><span class="nav-number">7.3.0.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">补充</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></div>
