态开始&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        orderDao.update(order.getUserId(),<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        log.info(<span class="string">&quot;-----&gt;修改订单状态结束&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">        log.info(<span class="string">&quot;-----&gt;下订单结束了&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
